        &lt;description&gt;For more info about how IntegrationHub works - https://docs.google.com/document/d/1x9ynIbonnTtx-a9h5CEiqyvlK-citlzcmaEp0HL3RiM/edit&amp;#13;
&amp;#13;
Business requirement:&amp;#13;
Our team uses slack for fast responses in the case of a High priority incident.&amp;#13;
Since we are also creating some incidents now in ServiceNow, we would like to share the description of any new High Priority incidents with ServiceNow together with a link via a message.&amp;#13;
We want to have a notification delivered if the service is down when it tries to send the message.&amp;#13;
&amp;#13;
Technical requirement:&amp;#13;
Make sure your instance has integrationHub activated.&amp;#13;
Create a flow which will trigger when a new High Priority incident is created.  This flow should use the Slack Webhook integrationhub spoke.&amp;#13;
Create a fallback when there is an error/timeout and test it.&amp;#13;
For testing purposes create an account on Slack, register a workspace, and channel and build a webhook.&lt;/description&gt;
